contentrichtext.text: {{Infobox French commune |name = Quaëdypre |image coat of arms = Blason de la ville de Socx (59) Nord-France.svg |region = [[Nord-Pas-de-Calais]] |department = Nord |arrondissement = Dunkerque |canton = Bergues |INSEE = 59478 |postal code = 59380 |mayor = André Remaux |term = 2008–2014 |intercommunality = canton de Bergues |longitude = 2.455 |latitude = 50.9367 |elevation m = 29 |elevation min m = 0 |elevation max m = 31 |area km2 = 18.7 |population = 1132 |population date = 2006 |demonym = Quaëdyprois, Quaëdyproises }} '''Quaëdypre''' ([[Dutch language|Dutch]]: ''Kwaadieper'') is a [[Communes of France|commune]] in the [[Nord (department)|Nord]] [[Departments of France|department]] in northern [[France]]. ==Heraldry== {{Blazon-arms | img1=Blason de la ville de Quaëdypre (59) Nord-France.svg | legend1=Arms of Quaëdypre | text=The arms of Quaëdypre are [[blazon]]ed :<br />{{SharedArms|Ar.lion.sa.bord}} }} ==See also== *[[Communes of the Nord department]] ==References== * [http://www.insee.fr/fr/methodes/nomenclatures/cog/fichecommunale.asp?codedep=59&codecom=478 INSEE commune file] {{Nord communes}} {{DEFAULTSORT:Quaedypre}} [[Category:Communes of Nord (French department)]] {{Nord-geo-stub}}
